        <h1>
            Hotel Taj Malabar, Cochin
            </h1>
        <!--pg-heading ends-->
        <div align="justify" class="txt">
            <img align="right" alt="Hotel Taj Malabar" height="209" src="images/hotel-taj-malabar.jpg"
                width="230" /><b>About Hotel :</b><br />
            <img border="0" height="1" hspace="0" src="http://www.kerala-tourism.net/gifs1/bdline.gif"
                vspace="2" width="243" /><br />
            Located on the waterfront, the hotel is just 15 minutes from the airport, and minutes
            away from the business district. The hotel has 108 rooms including 12 suites, which
            offer a spectacular view of the sea. Overall, the hotel offers a stunning view of
            the sea, harbor, backwaters of Cochin and of the sunset.
            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <b>Accommodation at Hotel Taj Malabar :</b><br />
            <img border="0" height="1" hspace="0" src="http://www.kerala-tourism.net/gifs1/bdline.gif"
                vspace="2" width="243" /><br />
            In all the Taj Malabar Hotel comprises of 97 rooms. There are 21 Harbour View Rooms,
            28 Sea View Rooms / 7 Sunset Rooms and 7 Executives Suites in the Tower Wing. The
            Heritage Wing comprises of 25 Superior Rooms, 6 Sea View Rooms/ 2 Deluxe Suites.<br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <b class="sh">Standard Rooms - </b>All rooms are elegantly appointed and offer guest
            amenities like with international direct dial facility, channel music and color
            television with satellite programs.
